Summary: Watching still over an hour NE of Anacortes very far away looks like a second much farther
divs: Sighting DetailsWatching a pulsating object about two hours all colors not moving, my cell can not pick up a photo, I see another to the East at a much further distance. It's pulsing all colors in pattern. can't be sure I think a black triangle underneath hard to tell. Will stay awake until it leaves.
